thread.title: Bruno & Angela
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Bruno & Angela

author: Bruno & Angela
title: Bruno & Angela
text:
Nelson Alexander certainly know the market well and offer a blue ribbon service. Through the highs and lows, Gordon was there to provide the right advice, contacts and knowledge and anything else that was required to steer the best course forward.
His rapport with potential buyers and negotiation skills shone through to provide the result we sought.
I have no hesitation in recommending others to entrust the sale of their home to him, in order to achieve the best outcome possible.
